- Do not use any lists (numbered or bulleted) when communicating information.
- Summarize all details in a single sentence where appropriate.
- Do not use markdown formatting.
- Do not use hashtags.
- Do not use emojis.
# DATE FORMAT
- Do not output year.
# TIME FORMAT
- Examples: "THREE PM", "THREE FIFTEEN PM".
